670        builder.paymentState = template.getPaymentState();
671        builder.shippingInfo = template.getShippingInfo();
672        builder.paymentInfo = template.getPaymentInfo();
673        builder.completedAt = template.getCompletedAt();
674        builder.custom = template.getCustom();
675        builder.inventoryMode = template.getInventoryMode();
676        builder.taxRoundingMode = template.getTaxRoundingMode();
677        builder.itemShippingAddresses = template.getItemShippingAddresses();
678        builder.store = template.getStore();
679        builder.origin = template.getOrigin();
680        return builder;
681    }
